User Authentication:

    POST /api/auth/register: Register a new user.
    POST /api/auth/login: Log in a user.
    GET /api/auth/profile: Get the authenticated user's profile (requires Bearer token).

Recipes:

    POST /api/recipes: Add a new recipe (authenticated, with image).
    GET /api/recipes: Get all recipes.
    GET /api/recipes/:id: Get recipe details by ID.

Ingredients:

    POST /api/ingredients: Add a new ingredient (authenticated, with image).
    GET /api/ingredients: Get all ingredient